{"tid":1071021,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本跟旅行團仲會唔會有導遊幫你ORDER自費美食","createTime":"2019-03-21T05:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T05:01:22.000Z","uid":159086,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"48bf014f270e23bc5e6ff152454e6d15ebd84626","tid":1071021,"uid":159086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T05:09:57.000Z","msg":"金槍魚魚腩<br />\n約12片(150g)~約16片(200g)<br />\n&yen;5200~&yen;7000<br />\n<br />\n刺身船<br />\n2至4人份量<br />\n&yen;9300~&yen;12500<br />\n<br />\n雞泡魚(河豚)<br />\n80g<br />\n&yen;6200<br />\n<br />\n喜知次<br />\n350g-400g<br />\n&yen;8700<br />\n<br />\n海膽<br />\n100g（塩水，折）<br />\n&yen;6000~&yen;7800<br />\n<br />\n帶子<br />\n1Kg<br />\n&yen;11000<br />\n<br />\n牡丹蝦<br />\n每隻<br />\n&yen;1000<br />\n<br />\n鱈場蟹<br />\n1Kg~3Kg<br />\n&yen;10500~&yen;27000<br />\n<br />\n毛蟹<br />\n500g~700g<br />\n&yen;8700~&yen;11500<br />\n<br />\n鮑魚<br />\n250~300g<br />\n&yen;7200~&yen;7800<br />\n<br />\n肉類<br />\n黑毛和牛<br />\n180g<br />\n&yen;8000<br />\n<br />\n松阪牛排<br />\n180g<br />\n&yen;12000<br />\n<br />\n黑豚豬排<br />\n180g<br />\n&yen;4800<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解資訊咁發達 點解仲可以食水咁深就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算跟市價都搵唔少啦 唔係抵買 仲要貴咁多<br />\n有沒人知貴市價幾多 就算同餐廳比都真係貴好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193312eef71eb7f304a3728f4c7ed84c24a98185","tid":1071021,"uid":5218,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:57:02.000Z","msg":"係囉，都識得講今時今日資訊發達去個日本都竟然要跟圍比導遊劏。"},{"pid":"ceca43a7529dd728beab4e4419f76e38ed3ae49b","tid":1071021,"uid":89931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T12:33:59.000Z","msg":"就係知道你喺2019年唔自己搵資料仲要跟旅行團 唔劏你劏邊個"},{"pid":"2f559b2d2841179286bf5f657dc4f5da8a49001b","tid":1071021,"uid":34949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T13:57:56.000Z","msg":"水魚價 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d580dc0717b8d66758c418a198484c72c8f0304a",